    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>English:</strong> One of the main features of this festival is the <em>sparrow dance</em>. I was told that this dance has over 2000 participants in the streets of Sendai. This dance is said to be created by Aoba castle&rsquo;s stone masons around 1600.</p>

